      "rationale": "FDA bench-test data include 4 independent bovine blood samples per operating point. Inter-sample CV ranges from 6% to 11% and is incorporated into the experimental uncertainty band. Sample preparation and storage protocols conform to ASTM F1841. Gradation 3 achieved."
